# Assets Loans And Receivables Term Excess Repayments Due To Sale Or Refinancing Amount

## identifier
de7628

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of term loans net of scheduled repayments, that are repaid in full during the relevant period as a result of the borrower either selling or refinancing the loan held by the reporting party.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.TermExcessRepaymentsDueToSaleOrRefinancing.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=duration
